# Founder collaboration

**Canon:** [`docs/SOP/FOUNDER_COLLABORATION_CHARTER_V1.md`](../../docs/SOP/FOUNDER_COLLABORATION_CHARTER_V1.md)

## Ongoing (no permanent thread)

Relationship lives in **pulses + charter doc**, not chat history. Founder opens **fresh** `THREAD_ROLE: founder_charter` only for monthly tweak or after a bad day. Daily: L1 ntfy · stalls: L3 ntfy · weekly: L4 digest. Last pulse: `artifacts/control_plane/FOUNDER_PULSE_LAST.json`.

## Pulses (never collapse layers)

| Layer | When | Shape |
|-------|------|--------|
| **L1 Morning** | Daily ~08:00 | Yesterday shipped + now state |
| **L2 Completion** | After slice/closeout/chapter step | 3–6 lines + "Nothing required from you." |
| **L3 Alert** | Blocked + no active program | **Alert:** plain language — immediate |
| **L4 Weekly** | Monday | `weekly_digest_monday.cmd` |

`ppe_founder_pulse.cmd --layer alert --write --notify`

## Bookkeeping (founder translation)

Four ledgers: **queue · marker · evidence · steering** (+ code on main). Deadlock = ledgers disagree, not "we didn't build." Diagram: charter § Bookkeeping for founders.

## Posture & closings

**Always building** unless asleep or missing direction SSOT. Default technical choices. One primary closing from charter § Agent reply contract — L3 overrides "nothing required."

## Thread type

`THREAD_ROLE: founder_charter` — relay **off**. Operator threads apply closings without opening charter thread.
